<p>I have quite strange issue when try to create the jump table in my asm program for iphone (arm64):</p>  <pre><code>.globl my_func my_func: ... //jump (switch) table .L.f_switch:     .short .L.case0 - .L.f_switch     .short .L.case1 - .L.f_switch     ... .L.case0: //some case code ... .L.case1: //other case code  </code></pre>  <p>After compilation this table is filled by zeros instead of actual values. It could be seen by dumping compiled object file.</p>  <pre><code>(__TEXT,__text) section _my_func: 0000000000000000    adr x4, #16 0000000000000004    ldrh    w5, [x4, x3, lsl #1] 0000000000000008    add x4, x4, w5, uxth 000000000000000c    br  x4 .L.f_switch: 0000000000000010    .long   0x00000000 0000000000000014    .long   0x00000000 0000000000000018    .long   0x00000000 000000000000001c    nop </code></pre>  <p>How to resolve it?</p>